---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { REPO_OWNER, REPO_NAME, VAGA_LABEL } from '../lib/github';
const postUrl = `https://github.com/${REPO_OWNER}/${REPO_NAME}/issues/new?labels=${VAGA_LABEL}&template=vaga.yml`;
---
<BaseLayout title="Ajuda" activeSection="ajuda" breadcrumb="ajuda/README.md">

<div class="doc-shell">

  <div class="doc-tabs">
    <div class="dtab active"><span class="td md"></span>README.md</div>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-area">
    <div class="doc-gutter" id="doc-gutter"></div>
    <div class="doc-content" id="doc-content">

      <div class="md-h1"># DevVagas — Como funciona</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <div class="md-p">
        O DevVagas usa o GitHub como infraestrutura completa: as vagas são criadas como
        <span class="md-code">Issues</span>, hospedadas via <span class="md-code">GitHub Pages</span>
        e implantadas automaticamente pelo <span class="md-code">GitHub Actions</span>.
      </div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>

      <div class="md-h2">## ⚡ Fluxo</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <div class="md-code-block">
        <div class="mcb-line"><span class="cmt">// o ciclo de vida de uma vaga</span></div>
        <div class="mcb-line"><span class="cb">Recrutador</span> abre Issue</div>
        <div class="mcb-line">  └→ GitHub Actions detecta evento</div>
        <div class="mcb-line">     └→ Astro faz rebuild estático</div>
        <div class="mcb-line">        └→ GitHub Pages publica (~1 min)</div>
        <div class="mcb-line">           └→ Vaga aparece no site ✓</div>
      </div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>

      <div class="md-h2">## 📋 Publicando uma vaga</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <div class="md-list">
        <div class="md-li"><span class="md-bullet">1.</span> Clique no botão abaixo ou acesse <span class="md-code">Issues → New Issue → Publicar Vaga</span></div>
        <div class="md-li"><span class="md-bullet">2.</span> Preencha o formulário com os campos abaixo</div>
        <div class="md-li"><span class="md-bullet">3.</span> Marque a caixa de confirmação e clique em <span class="md-code">Submit new issue</span></div>
        <div class="md-li"><span class="md-bullet">4.</span> Aguarde ~1 minuto para a vaga aparecer no site</div>
      </div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>

      <div class="md-h3">### Campos do formulário</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <div class="md-fields">
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Empresa <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Nome da empresa. Ex: <span class="md-code">Nubank</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Nível <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Selecione: <span class="md-code">Júnior</span> · <span class="md-code">Pleno</span> · <span class="md-code">Sênior</span> · <span class="md-code">Lead</span> · <span class="md-code">Especialista</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Área <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Selecione: <span class="md-code">Dev</span> · <span class="md-code">Business</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Tipo <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Selecione: <span class="md-code">Remoto</span> · <span class="md-code">Híbrido</span> · <span class="md-code">Presencial</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Localização <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Cidade/Estado ou "Remoto BR". Ex: <span class="md-code">São Paulo/SP</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Salário</span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Faixa salarial ou "A combinar". Ex: <span class="md-code">R$ 10k–15k</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Stack <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Tecnologias separadas por vírgula. Ex: <span class="md-code">React, TypeScript, Node.js</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Descrição <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Sobre a empresa, responsabilidades, requisitos e benefícios</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Candidatura <span class="mf-req">*</span></span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Link ou e-mail para candidatura. Ex: <span class="md-code">https://empresa.com/vagas</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">LinkedIn?</span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Selecione <span class="md-code">Sim</span> se a vaga está publicada no LinkedIn</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mf-row">
          <span class="mf-field">Internacional?</span>
          <span class="mf-desc">Selecione <span class="md-code">Sim</span> se a vaga é aberta para candidatos internacionais ou é de empresa estrangeira</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md-hint"><span class="mf-req">*</span> campo obrigatório</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <a href={postUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="md-cta">
        → Publicar vaga agora
      </a>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>

      <div class="md-h2">## 🔒 Fechando uma vaga</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <div class="md-p">Para remover uma vaga do site, basta <strong>fechar a Issue</strong> correspondente no GitHub. O site atualiza automaticamente.</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>
      <div class="md-p">Você também pode pausar temporariamente removendo a label <span class="md-code">vaga</span> sem fechar a issue.</div>
      <div class="md-blank"></div>

      <div style="height:4rem"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.doc-shell {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  height: calc(100vh - 36px - 24px);
}

.doc-tabs {
  display: flex; background: var(--darker);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); height: 36px; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.dtab {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
  padding: 0 1rem; height: 100%;
  font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-top: 2px solid var(--cyan);
  background: var(--black);
}
.td { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }
.td.md { background: #6b7280; }

.doc-area {
  display: flex; flex: 1; overflow: hidden;
}

.doc-gutter {
  width: 44px; background: var(--darker);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border); flex-shrink: 0;
}

.doc-content {
  flex: 1; overflow-y: auto;
  padding: 1.5rem 3rem; max-width: 820px;
}

.md-h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.md-h2 {
  font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cyan);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;
}
.md-p { font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #8aacca; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.md-p strong { color: var(--text); }
.md-blank { height: 0.5rem; }
.md-code {
  font-family: var(--font); background: var(--mid);
  border: 1px solid var(--border2); color: var(--cyan);
  padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem; font-size: 0.85em;
}

.md-code-block {
  background: var(--darker); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
  padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.72rem; line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.mcb-line { display: block; }
.cmt { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
.cb  { color: #569cd6; }

.md-list { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.md-li { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8aacca; line-height: 1.8; }
.md-bullet { color: var(--green); flex-shrink: 0; width: 1.2rem; }

.md-h3 {
  font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;
}

.md-fields {
  border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.72rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.mf-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
  padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem; gap: 1rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  align-items: baseline;
}
.mf-row:last-child { border: none; }
.mf-field { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
.mf-req { color: var(--red, #f87171); font-size: 0.75em; }
.mf-desc { color: #8aacca; line-height: 1.6; }

.md-hint {
  font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.md-cta {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center;
  background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--green);
  color: var(--green); padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  transition: all 0.2s; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.md-cta::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: var(--green); transform: translateX(-101%);
  transition: transform 0.2s; z-index: 0;
}
.md-cta:hover { color: var(--black); }
.md-cta:hover::before { transform: none; }
.md-cta > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.md-table {
  border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.7rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.mt-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; gap: 1rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.mt-row:last-child { border: none; }
.mt-head { background: var(--darker); color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.62rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.green  { color: var(--green); }
.yellow { color: var(--yellow); }
</style>

<script>
  const content = document.getElementById('doc-content')!;
  const gutter  = document.getElementById('doc-gutter')!;
  const lineH   = 0.72 * 16 * 1.9;
  const count   = Math.ceil((content.scrollHeight || 600) / lineH) + 10;
  gutter.innerHTML = Array.from({length: Math.max(count, 40)}, (_, i) =>
    `<div style="font-size:0.6rem;color:var(--muted2);text-align:right;padding-right:0.6rem;line-height:${lineH}px">${i+1}</div>`
  ).join('');
  content.addEventListener('scroll', () => { gutter.scrollTop = content.scrollTop; });
</script>
